{
  "script_id": "absolute-value",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "这节课我们认识一个很特别的函数，绝对值函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "它的图像不是平滑的曲线，而是一条尖尖的 V 形折线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "要理解它，我们先从绝对值的含义说起。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "concept-abs",
      "line_id": "abs-1",
      "filename": "concept-abs-abs-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/concept-abs-abs-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "一个数的绝对值，就是它在数轴上到零点的距离。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "concept-abs",
      "line_id": "abs-2",
      "filename": "concept-abs-abs-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/concept-abs-abs-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.72,
      "size": 43488,
      "text": "距离永远不会是负的，所以正三的绝对值是三，负三的绝对值也是三。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "concept-abs",
      "line_id": "abs-3",
      "filename": "concept-abs-abs-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/concept-abs-abs-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.71,
      "size": 43344,
      "text": "把每个横坐标都取绝对值当作高度，图像就在原点两侧对称地往上翘。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "concept-shape",
      "line_id": "shape-1",
      "filename": "concept-shape-shape-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/concept-shape-shape-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "最基本的 y 等于 x 的绝对值，图像是一个开口向上的 V 字。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "concept-shape",
      "line_id": "shape-2",
      "filename": "concept-shape-shape-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/concept-shape-shape-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "V 字最低的那个尖角叫做顶点，这里的顶点正好落在原点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "concept-shape",
      "line_id": "shape-3",
      "filename": "concept-shape-shape-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/concept-shape-shape-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "左右两条边都是直线，关于经过顶点的竖直线完全对称。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "concept-transform",
      "line_id": "trans-1",
      "filename": "concept-transform-trans-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/concept-transform-trans-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "在绝对值里减去一个数，图像就会整体向右平移。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "concept-transform",
      "line_id": "trans-2",
      "filename": "concept-transform-trans-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/concept-transform-trans-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "在外面加上一个数，整条 V 形就会向上抬升。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "concept-transform",
      "line_id": "trans-3",
      "filename": "concept-transform-trans-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/concept-transform-trans-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.82,
      "size": 45072,
      "text": "前面乘上一个系数，正数让开口变窄变陡，负数则让 V 形倒过来开口向下。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "试着切换不同的参数，看看顶点跑到哪里，开口是宽是窄。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "当 V 形跨过横轴时，两个交点就是方程的解，也就是函数的零点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "绝对值表示到零的距离，所以图像是对称的 V 形折线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "顶点的位置由平移决定，开口方向和陡缓由系数决定。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "absolute-value",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/absolute-value/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "数与形结合，绝对值函数就一目了然，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 36.010000000000005,
